trans-unit.source: Represents a size measurement in a log store policy.
trans-unit.target: Representerer et størrelse mål i en policy for lagring av loggen.

trans-unit.source: The PolicyUnit structure represents a size measurement in a log store policy.
trans-unit.target: PolicyUnit-struktur representerer et størrelse mål i en policy for lagring av loggen.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.IO.Log.PolicyUnitType> enumeration lists the units of measurement that can be represented.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.IO.Log.PolicyUnitType>opplisting viser målenheten som kan representeres.</xref:System.IO.Log.PolicyUnitType>

trans-unit.source: You can use the <xref:System.IO.Log.PolicyUnit.Value%2A> property to determine the size of the measurement.
trans-unit.target: Du kan bruke den <xref:System.IO.Log.PolicyUnit.Value%2A>til å fastsette størrelsen på målingen.</xref:System.IO.Log.PolicyUnit.Value%2A>

trans-unit.source: To determine the unit of measurement, use the <xref:System.IO.Log.PolicyUnit.Type%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Bruk til å fastslå målenheten den <xref:System.IO.Log.PolicyUnit.Type%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.IO.Log.PolicyUnit.Type%2A>

trans-unit.source: You can convert other data types to a PolicyUnit by using the <xref:System.IO.Log.PolicyUnit.Percentage%2A> and <xref:System.IO.Log.PolicyUnit.Extents%2A> methods.
trans-unit.target: Kan du konvertere andre datatyper til en PolicyUnit ved hjelp av den <xref:System.IO.Log.PolicyUnit.Percentage%2A>og <xref:System.IO.Log.PolicyUnit.Extents%2A>metoder.</xref:System.IO.Log.PolicyUnit.Extents%2A> </xref:System.IO.Log.PolicyUnit.Percentage%2A>
